metadata.name: Mother I (2012) Remastered
metadata.description:
Mother I (2012) Remastered 

With more than 1.215.641 million Views in Giphy since the first upload "Mother" is a series of ethereal portraits created in 2012 in the Tumblr Community with  size and color limitations, Now remastered  with full 1080x1080 HD and Sound. 

Special content included:
Original gif.
Audio commentary and notes. 
1 poster RTP signed.
